Quality Payment Program

Source: R/end_qpp.R
quality_payment.Rd

Quality Payment Program

Usage

qpp_stats(year)

qpp_elig(year, npi)

Arguments

year

A vector of years from 2018 to 2025

npi

A vector of NPIs

Examples

qpp_stats(year = 2018:2025) |> print(n = Inf)
